  <prompt>
    Author a new `sprk_chartdefinition` Dataverse record named `Matter Budget` per FR-DV-02. Visual Type = `HorizontalStackedBar` (100000012), Entity = `sprk_matter`. Data fields: `sprk_totalspendtodate` (current) + `sprk_totalbudget` (total). Provide the exact `sprk_optionsjson` payload below. Configure Drill Through to `sprk_invoice` filtered by `_sprk_matter_value`. Verify the chart renders correctly on a Matter record with financial data via a Visual Host instance bound to this chart def.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Dataverse configurator with familiarity with the Visual Host chart-definition contract and the `sprk_chartdefinition` schema. Comfortable using the Dataverse MCP (`create_record` / `read_query`) or PowerShell + Web API to author records.
  </role>

  <goal>
    A single `sprk_chartdefinition` record exists in Dataverse named `Matter Budget` with the exact `sprk_optionsjson` from FR-DV-02, Drill Through set to `sprk_invoice` filtered by `_sprk_matter_value`. A test Visual Host instance bound to this chart def on a Matter record renders `$50K` headline + `33% of $150K` sub-line + a color-thresholded horizontal progress bar matching the Variant H prototype.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      FR-DV-02 depends on the renderer changes shipped in task 023 (FR-VH-04: `layoutMode: "headlineAboveBar"`, `headlineFromField`, `subLineTemplate` with `{remaining}` / `{percent}` / `{total}` placeholders, suppression of the existing top-right total + bottom-right remaining labels). Per §6.4.0 (binding), this MUST use the existing HorizontalStackedBar visual type and the new generic Custom Options keys only — no Matter-specific paths in Visual Host. NFR-05 backward compatibility is the renderer's responsibility (task 025).
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>docs/architecture/VISUALHOST-ARCHITECTURE.md</file>
      <file>docs/guides/VISUALHOST-SETUP-GUIDE.md</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/components/HorizontalStackedBar.tsx</file>
      <file>src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/components/ChartRenderer.tsx</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec">FR-DV-02 — visual type HorizontalStackedBar (100000012); entity sprk_matter; exact sprk_optionsjson payload</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">§6.4.0 (binding) — no new visual types; use only HSBar + new generic Custom Options keys delivered by task 023</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">NFR-05 — existing chart defs unchanged (renderer-layer concern; verified in task 025)</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 tokens applied via the renderer; token-set names (success/warning/danger) are renderer-resolved</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>docs/architecture/VISUALHOST-ARCHITECTURE.md</file>
