  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">A single active sprk_chartdefinition record named "Matter Budget" exists with sprk_visualtype = 100000012 and sprk_entityname = "sprk_matter".</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">sprk_optionsjson round-trips byte-identically to the payload in the notes block below.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Render verification (FR-DV-02 Acceptance): chart renders `$50K`-style headline + `33% of $150K`-style sub-line + colored progress bar; expand opens invoice list filtered to current matter.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">TASK-INDEX.md shows 031 as ✅ completed.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Exact sprk_optionsjson payload per spec FR-DV-02:

    ```json
    {
      "valueFormat": "currency",
      "layoutMode": "headlineAboveBar",
      "headlineFromField": "sprk_totalspendtodate",
      "subLineTemplate": "{percent}% of {total}",
      "colorThresholds": [
        { "range": [0.0, 0.6], "tokenSet": "success" },
        { "range": [0.6, 0.85], "tokenSet": "warning" },
        { "range": [0.85, 1.0], "tokenSet": "danger" }
      ]
    }
    ```

    Data binding: `sprk_totalspendtodate` (current) + `sprk_totalbudget` (total) — both fields are existing rollups on `sprk_matter` per Phase A.5 recon; no schema change needed.
  </notes>

